text.section:
This subtitle does not apply to:
an officer, employee, insurance producer, or other representative of an authorized insurer while acting for the authorized insurer;
an insurance producer that holds a license while acting as an insurance producer for a client;
an attorney at law of the State while acting within the scope of the legal profession;
a licensed public adjuster while acting within the scope of the public adjuster's license; and
an individual:
who is employed by an investment adviser registered with the Securities and Exchange Commission;
whose only clients in the State each:
whose business activities in the State that would otherwise be subject to regulation under this subtitle are limited to acting as an adviser with respect to guaranteed investment contracts or synthetic investment contracts.
